OL,3,CWater supplies restored after
OL,4,Cthousands face issues over weekend
OL,6,FThousands of people in Kent have had
OL,7,Fwater supplies restored after issues
OL,8,Fover the weekend, according to South
OL,9,FEast Water (SEW).
OL,11,FThe company said on Saturday that
OL,12,F7,000 properties around the Tunbridge
OL,13,FWells area faced supply issues
OL,14,Fincluding low pressure, intermittent
OL,15,Fsupply or no water after an
OL,16,F"instrument failure" at a nearby
OL,17,Ftreatment works.
OL,19,FOn Sunday evening, SEW said supplies
OL,20,Fhad been restored to customers in the
OL,21,FTunbridge Wells and Pembury areas.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
