OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784569706
OL,3,CWater supplies restored after
OL,4,Cthousands face issues over weekend
OL,6,FSEW incident manager Steve Benton
OL,7,Fapologised to customers, saying: "This
OL,8,Fis not the service we aim to provide,
OL,9,Fand is not the service our customers
OL,10,Fdeserve."
OL,12,FBottled water stations were set up by
OL,13,Fthe company over the weekend in the
OL,14,Faffected areas.
OL,16,FEarlier this week, the utility was
OL,17,Fordered to pay #30.5 million after
OL,18,Finvestigations by Ofwat.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
