PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784569706
OL,3,CWater supplies restored after
OL,4,Cthousands face issues over weekend
OL,6,FThe industry watchdog launched the
OL,7,Fprobe following previous supply
OL,8,Finterruptions, affecting hundreds of
OL,9,Fthousands of households across Kent
OL,10,Fand Sussex.
OL,12,FOfwat said the redress package
OL,13,Fconcludes three investigations into
OL,14,Fthe supplier and includes a previously
OL,15,Fproposed #22 million fine for water
OL,16,Fsupply failures between 2020 and 2023,
OL,17,Fwhich impacted more than 286,000
OL,18,Fpeople.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
