OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784569706
OL,3,CWater supplies restored after
OL,4,Cthousands face issues over weekend
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe regulator launched a second probe
OL,12,Fat the start of this year after
OL,13,Ffurther supply interruptions in
OL,14,FTunbridge Wells and across Kent and
OL,15,FSussex between November and January,
OL,16,Fwhich left up to 70,000 homes without
OL,17,Fwater.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
