PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784569706
OL,3,CWater supplies restored after
OL,4,Cthousands face issues over weekend
OL,6,FThe third investigation followed the
OL,7,Fdowngrading of SEW's credit rating by
OL,8,FMoody's in May, which meant the firm
OL,9,Fwas in breach of its licence condition.
OL,11,FSEW warned in its annual report this
OL,12,Fweek that it needed to secure fresh
OL,13,Ffinancing to stay afloat after taking
OL,14,Fa #55 million hit from outages over
OL,15,Fthe winter.
OL,17,FThe water supplier, which has around
OL,18,F2.3 million customers in the South
OL,19,FEast, said it was in discussions with
OL,20,Flenders to agree a new loan facility.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
