PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784569706
OL,3,CWater supplies restored after
OL,4,Cthousands face issues over weekend
OL,6,FIt has enough cash to keep going until
OL,7,FJuly 2027, but flagged that "shortly
OL,8,Fafter" it will need to get more
OL,9,Ffinancing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
